file.name: error_http_api_null_method.yaml
file.content:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
Resources:
  MyHttpApiGateway:
    Type: AWS::Serverless::HttpApi
    Properties:
      Auth:
        Authorizers:
          MyAuthorizer:
            IdentitySource: $request.header.Authorization
            JwtConfiguration:
              issuer:
                Ref: MyOAuth2Issuer
        DefaultAuthorizer: MyAuthorizer
      DefinitionBody:
        openapi: 3.0.1
        paths:
          /test:
            post: null
